> * `handle_binding_changed()` that reacts to the `kBindingsChangedViaCluster` event.  
> * A tiny subscription manager (`gActiveSubs`).  

All other parts of your original code (window‑covering command handlers, GPIO handling, LED indicator, etc.) stay exactly the same.

