### Final Thought

All of the heavy lifting (CASE session, TLV encoding/decoding, subscription resumption) is already handled by the **Esp‑Matter client APIs** you included. By wiring the **Binding‑changed event** to a **subscription manager**, installing a **validator on the Bind command**, and providing a **ReadClient callback** that drives your GPIOs, you get a **robust, stateless shade controller** that reacts to any remote contact sensor without needing a motor‑position feedback loop.

